fields.title: 1990 census of population and housing. Public Law 94-171 data. Arizona, Georgia, Michigan, New Hampshire, North Dakota, Wisconsin

dsDescription.dsDescriptionValue:
1 computer laser optical disc ; 4 3/4 in.

CDRM 454600

Hierarchical file structure.ISO 9660 format.

Provides census data designed and formatted for use in legislative redistricting. Census counts, for areas as small as blocks, census tracts, and voting districts, include totals for population, race groups, persons of Hispanic origin, population 18 years and over, and housing units.
